body:
## 🐛 Bug Report

<!-- A clear and concise description of what the bug is. --> The Developer Tools not showing at start and can't be launched from Menu Panel (Toggle Developer Tools).

Lib version: 4.3.0

## Steps To Reproduce

1. Run app with `const ExcelJS = require('exceljs');` code.

```const { app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain, shell, Notification } = require('electron');
const path = require('path');
const date = require('date-and-time');
// const fs = require('fs');
const cmd = require('node-cmd');

// const {getDesktopFolder} = require('platform-folders');

let windowsClosedIf = false;
let values1toIpcRenderer = {};
let sendToIpcRenderer = false;

const ExcelJS = require('exceljs');

const createWindow = () => {
  // Create the browser window
	const mainWindow = new BrowserWindow({
		// frame: false,
		autoHideMenuBar: false,
		width: 1200,
		height: 650,
		icon: __dirname + '/files/icon.ico',
		webPreferences: {
			nodeIntegration: true,
			contextIsolation: false
		}
	});

	// Load index.html (primary file) to app
	mainWindow.loadFile(path.join(__dirname, 'index.html'));
	
	mainWindow.webContents.openDevTools();	
	// mainWindow.webContents.setDevToolsWebContents(devtools.webContents);
//   mainWindow.webContents.openDevTools({ mode: 'detach' });
		
	setInterval(() => {
		if (windowsClosedIf == false){
			if (sendToIpcRenderer == true){
				mainWindow.webContents.send('valuesProbki', values1toIpcRenderer);
				values1toIpcRenderer = {};
				sendToIpcRenderer = false;
			}
		}
	},500);
};

// If Electron is ready, create windows
app.on('ready', createWindow);

// If all windows are closed do...
app.on('window-all-closed', () => {
	windowsClosedIf = true;
	app.quit();
});
```

## The expected behaviour:

Developer Tools panel can be opened by user from Menu or can be started automatically when application starts.


## Possible solution (optional, but very helpful):

Comment the line `const ExcelJS = require('exceljs');` and DevTools window opens automatically and works correct.


